OL,3,CMan guilty of failed spy plot to share
OL,4,Cinformation about Sir Grant Shapps
OL,6,FA man from Harlow, who was
OL,7,F"infatuated" with Mi5 and James Bond
OL,8,Fhas been found guilty of trying to
OL,9,Fgive information to people he thought
OL,10,Fwere Russian spies - but who were
OL,11,Factually undercover British agents.
OL,13,FHoward Phillips, 65, intended to help
OL,14,Ftwo apparent Russian agents called
OL,15,F"Sasha" and "Dima", by passing on
OL,16,Fpersonal information about former
OL,17,Fdefence secretary Sir Grant Shapps.
OL,19,FHe also was helping the pair with
OL,20,Ftravel logistics and booking hotels.
