OL,3,CMan guilty of failed spy plot to share
OL,4,Cinformation about Sir Grant Shapps
OL,6,FBut "Dima" and "Sasha" were in fact
OL,7,Fundercover British intelligence
OL,8,Fofficers, Winchester Crown Court heard.
OL,10,FA jury found Phillips guilty of
OL,11,Fassisting a foreign intelligence
OL,12,Fservice under the National Security
OL,13,FAct on Tuesday, following a trial at
OL,14,Fthe same court.
OL,16,FThe jury reached a unanimous verdict
OL,17,Fafter four hours and four minutes of
OL,18,Fdeliberations.
