OL,3,CMan guilty of failed spy plot to share
OL,4,Cinformation about Sir Grant Shapps
OL,6,FPhillips, wearing a dark suit and tie,
OL,7,Fsilently shook his head in the dock as
OL,8,Fthe verdict was given.
OL,10,FThe defendant's ex-wife, Amanda
OL,11,FPhillips, told the court during the
OL,12,Ftrial that he "would dream about being
OL,13,Flike James Bond", and that he watched
OL,14,Ffilms to do with MI5 and MI6 as he was
OL,15,F"infatuated with it".
