OL,6,FMrs Phillips told the court she was
OL,7,Faware the defendant had applied for a
OL,8,Fjob at the UK Border Force in October
OL,9,F2023, which prosecutors said was part
OL,10,Fof his bid to assist Russia's
OL,11,Fintelligence service.
OL,13,FPhillips previously claimed he had
OL,14,Fcontacted the Russian embassy in early
OL,15,F2024 in a bid to track and expose
OL,16,FRussian agents to assist Israel.
OL,18,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb remanded
OL,19,FPhillips in custody and adjourned
OL,20,Fsentencing to the "earliest available
OL,21,Fdate" in the autumn.
